#lg D	uru


@(62-64=c25402.D.62) Good woman, daughter of @wDN{An}, @wDN{Enlil} has called for you! …… the holy shining throne-dais …… told you; young woman, Mother @wDN{Bau}, the daughter of @wDN{An}, @wDN{Enlil} has called for you! …… the holy shining throne-dais …… told you: @q{“Bestow on @wRN{Išme-@wDN{Dagan}}, the son of @wDN{Enlil}, a life of numerous days!”}

